<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٧٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(لا يصلون إلا بإقامة)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> لو أدركهم عمر بن الخطاب <span class="c2">(لأوجعهم)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">(ضربا)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span> أو لأوجع رؤوسهم.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
